{"tid":2493603,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「匪情研究」前世今生｜習上台後大陸研究好難做 台學者為香港失自由感沉痛","createTime":"2021-04-18T04:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T05:30:37.000Z","uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a897bbe43d94b47af3962b6aeb83c10a8ab98116","tid":2493603,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:46:59.000Z","msg":"「匪情研究」前世今生｜習上台後大陸研究好難做 台學者為香港失自由感沉痛<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210403/CP4APCF3BJG3BJWNUA4NUNEK7Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210403%2FCP4APCF3BJG3BJWNUA4NUNEK7Q%2F&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RL3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=ce0c0a71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210403%2FCP4APCF3BJG3BJWNUA4NUNEK7Q%2F&h=c8d5e245\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210403/CP4APCF3BJG3BJWNUA4NUNEK7Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n王信賢又謂，不只台灣，甚至西方社會對中國大陸的掌握，都變得越來越困難。而大陸對台灣，從傳統的「統戰」，發展至近年的「認知作戰」（cognitive warfare），透過發放真假難辨的訊息，擾亂民心、製造紛亂，王信賢覺得北京的「作戰」對象，其實不限於台灣，同時包括南韓、日本、美國及澳洲等地方。他說：「那我覺得，台灣在這個部份（大陸的認知作戰）應該已是比較習慣，畢竟並非這幾年的事，其實這種互動，兩岸從1949年開始已存在。台灣政府及人民對大陸的防範，都有一點警覺性。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對於香港選舉制度被北京「閹割」後，又要面對大陸在教育等方面全方位意識形態操控，王信賢並不樂觀。「北京現在的做法是另起爐灶，要打掉重練，它要從頭抓起，比現在年輕人更年輕的一代，要從頭做起。」他續說：「除非你移民他國，對於曾經參與反送中這一代年輕人，從台灣人的角度來說，北京做法或會更嚴格......講起來，也有點沉痛。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a2bbece13c86651e45b360202264cdffa8ff9f2","tid":2493603,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:48:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaRXXHF6LVRoNuG2bVy4schDiX3t6Jt6r13dQnuTXA5Fn?filename=ANGr2GX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FANGr2GX.png&h=017d56af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac04294b8e70b27c614d79bc2110450768120f21","tid":2493603,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:49:34.000Z","msg":"砍掉重練"},{"pid":"24bfbd4934a40bb1ccfa6544b09fa976fdd0b398","tid":2493603,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:50:41.000Z","msg":"研究習近平好簡單，佢目標就係超越毛澤東，做21世紀嘅秦皇漢武 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be60054bd5c2d3dcfa0eff38c237e44943d9c29b","tid":2493603,"uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:53:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>它要從頭抓起，比現在年輕人更年輕的一代，要從頭做起。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(有圖) 今日有班小學生係到重演831<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2490197\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2490197</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNhuRJXKjUekN5iVJjXJxUmXazbWbrZyBD2eDhk7a1ViQ?filename=Ns3uVFL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNs3uVFL.jpg&h=53d04786&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5be450cd52bfccdb6b013ab0416538ce57bf299","tid":2493603,"uid":301952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:59:06.000Z","msg":"由2000年雙非案，刻意留下法律漏洞唔解決，到2003年689自由行導致衝關漏洞，到2009年IANG暴增，呢代人要被換血，係由佢小學生，甚至只係精子一刻就已經被決定，有冇反送中係冇分別，關鍵係支共上至政權，下至十三億人都係妒忌貪婪香港人既成就，要鵲巢鳩占，要踩死原來存在既人"},{"pid":"510550086f81bdc909082f1095552c4a9d22251b","tid":2493603,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4a2bbece13c86651e45b360202264cdffa8ff9f2","tid":2493603,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:48:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ANGr2GX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FANGr2GX.png&h=017d56af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hk